<p />
<h1><a name="Upgrading_Fetch_Crl_2_to_Fetch_C"></a>  Upgrading Fetch-Crl 2 to Fetch-Crl 3 on EL5 (preview) </h1>
<div class="twikiToc"> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#Procedure"> Procedure</a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Translation_table_from_fetch_crl"> Translation table from fetch-crl.conf to fetch-crl3.conf:</a>
</li></ul> 
</div>
<p />
<h2 class="twikinetRoundedAttachments"><span class="twikinetHeader"><a name="Procedure"></a> Procedure </span></h2>
<p /> <ol>
<li> <code>service disable fetch-crl-{boot,cron}</code>
</li> <li> Either <code>yum install fetch-crl3</code> or <code>yum upgrade</code> any package that used to require <code>fetch-crl</code> (see above lists)
</li> <li> <code>service enable fetch-crl3-{boot,cron}</code>
</li> <li> Edit <code>/etc/cron.d/fetch-crl3</code> to change parameters if desired (it's marked as a &#37;config file in the rpm)
</li> <li> Edit <code>/etc/fetch-crl3.conf</code> as desired, see table
</li> <li> Test it; once satisfied that it works, you can <code>yum erase fetch-crl</code> to get rid of the old version
</li></ol> 
<p />
<h2 class="twikinetRoundedAttachments"><span class="twikinetHeader"><a name="Translation_table_from_fetch_crl"></a> <strong>Translation table from fetch-crl.conf to fetch-crl3.conf:</strong> </span></h2>
<p />
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" class="twikinetWrapperTable" rules="none">
<tr class="twikinetWrapperTableRow">
<td class="twikinetWrapperTableT twikinetWrapperTableTL"></td>
<td class="twikinetWrapperTableT twikinetWrapperTableTR"></td>
</tr>
<tr class="twikinetWrapperTableRow">
<td colspan="2" class="twikinetWrapperTableMain">
<table cellspacing="0" id="table1" cellpadding="0" class="twikiTable" rules="cols" border="1">
		<tr class="twikiTableOdd twikiTableRowdataBgSorted0 twikiTableRowdataBg0">
			<th bgcolor="#d8dde4" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol0 twikiFirstCol"> <a rel="nofollow" href="/bin/view/Documentation/UpgradeFetchCrl2to3_Preview?cover=print;sortcol=0;table=1;up=0#sorted_table" title="Sort by this column"><font color="#252b37">fetch-crl.conf</font></a> </th>
			<th bgcolor="#d8dde4" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol1 twikiLastCol"> <a rel="nofollow" href="/bin/view/Documentation/UpgradeFetchCrl2to3_Preview?cover=print;sortcol=1;table=1;up=0#sorted_table" title="Sort by this column"><font color="#252b37">fetch-crl3.conf</font></a> </th>
		</tr>
		<tr class="twikiTableEven twikiTableRowdataBgSorted0 twikiTableRowdataBg0">
			<td bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol0 twikiFirstCol"> <code>ALLWARNINGS=yes</code> </td>
			<td bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol1 twikiLastCol"> can't be set, but see <code>nowarnings</code> and <code>verbosity</code> </td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="twikiTableOdd twikiTableRowdataBgSorted1 twikiTableRowdataBg1">
			<td bgcolor="#f2f3f6" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol0 twikiFirstCol"> <code>CACHEDIR=/var/cache/fetch-crl</code> </td>
			<td bgcolor="#f2f3f6" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol1 twikiLastCol"> <code>statedir = /var/cache/fetch-crl3</code> (I think?) </td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="twikiTableEven twikiTableRowdataBgSorted0 twikiTableRowdataBg0">
			<td bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol0 twikiFirstCol"> <code>CACHEDIR=</code> (disables cache) </td>
			<td bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol1 twikiLastCol"> <code>nocache</code> or <code>stateless</code> (those aren't synonyms but I don't know what the difference is) </td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="twikiTableOdd twikiTableRowdataBgSorted1 twikiTableRowdataBg1">
			<td bgcolor="#f2f3f6" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol0 twikiFirstCol"> <code>CRLDIR=/etc/grid-security-certificates</code> </td>
			<td bgcolor="#f2f3f6" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol1 twikiLastCol"> <code>infodir = /etc/grid-security/certificates</code> </td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="twikiTableEven twikiTableRowdataBgSorted0 twikiTableRowdataBg0">
			<td bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol0 twikiFirstCol"> <code>CRL_AGING_THRESHOLD=24</code> </td>
			<td bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol1 twikiLastCol"> <code>agingtolerance = 24</code> </td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="twikiTableOdd twikiTableRowdataBgSorted1 twikiTableRowdataBg1">
			<td bgcolor="#f2f3f6" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol0 twikiFirstCol"> <code>FETCH_CRL_OPENSSL=/usr/bin/openssl</code> </td>
			<td bgcolor="#f2f3f6" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol1 twikiLastCol"> <code>openssl = /usr/bin/openssl</code> </td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="twikiTableEven twikiTableRowdataBgSorted0 twikiTableRowdataBg0">
			<td bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol0 twikiFirstCol"> <code>FORCE_OVERWRITE=yes</code> </td>
			<td bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol1 twikiLastCol"> always 'yes' </td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="twikiTableOdd twikiTableRowdataBgSorted1 twikiTableRowdataBg1">
			<td bgcolor="#f2f3f6" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol0 twikiFirstCol"> <code>HTTP_PROXY=...</code> </td>
			<td bgcolor="#f2f3f6" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol1 twikiLastCol"> <code>http_proxy = ...</code> or set in <code>/etc/sysconfig/fetch-crl3</code> and use <code>http_proxy = ENV</code> </td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="twikiTableEven twikiTableRowdataBgSorted0 twikiTableRowdataBg0">
			<td bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol0 twikiFirstCol"> <code>QUIET=yes</code> </td>
			<td bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol1 twikiLastCol"> <code>verbosity = -1</code> </td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="twikiTableOdd twikiTableRowdataBgSorted1 twikiTableRowdataBg1">
			<td bgcolor="#f2f3f6" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol0 twikiFirstCol"> <code>RESETPATHMODE=yes</code> </td>
			<td bgcolor="#f2f3f6" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol1 twikiLastCol"> <code>path = /bin:/usr/bin</code> </td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="twikiTableEven twikiTableRowdataBgSorted0 twikiTableRowdataBg0">
			<td bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol0 twikiFirstCol"> <code>RESETPATHMODE=searchopenssl</code> </td>
			<td bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol1 twikiLastCol"> ? </td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="twikiTableOdd twikiTableRowdataBgSorted1 twikiTableRowdataBg1">
			<td bgcolor="#f2f3f6" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol0 twikiFirstCol"> <code>SERVERCERTCHECK=no</code> </td>
			<td bgcolor="#f2f3f6" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol1 twikiLastCol"> always 'no'; install <code>perl-Crypt-SSLeay</code> and set <code>HTTPS_CA_FILE</code> in <code>/etc/sysconfig/fetch-crl3</code> if you want to check server cert, but the docs suggest that since the crls are signed, checking server cert is unnecessary and may give false positives for security warnings </td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="twikiTableEven twikiTableRowdataBgSorted0 twikiTableRowdataBg0">
			<td bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol0 twikiFirstCol"> <code>SLOPPYCRLHASHES=yes</code> </td>
			<td bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol1 twikiLastCol"> can't be set </td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="twikiTableOdd twikiTableRowdataBgSorted1 twikiTableRowdataBg1">
			<td bgcolor="#f2f3f6" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol0 twikiFirstCol"> <code>SYSLOGFACILITY=daemon</code> </td>
			<td bgcolor="#f2f3f6" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol1 twikiLastCol"> <code>syslogfacility = daemon </td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="twikiTableEven twikiTableRowdataBgSorted0 twikiTableRowdataBg0">
			<td bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol0 twikiFirstCol"> <code>WGET_OPTS=...</code> </td>
			<td bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol1 twikiLastCol"> can't be set </td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="twikiTableOdd twikiTableRowdataBgSorted1 twikiTableRowdataBg1">
			<td bgcolor="#f2f3f6" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol0 twikiFirstCol"> <code>WGET_RETRIES=2</code> </td>
			<td bgcolor="#f2f3f6" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol1 twikiLastCol"> can't be set </td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="twikiTableEven twikiTableRowdataBgSorted0 twikiTableRowdataBg0">
			<td bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol0 twikiFirstCol twikiLast"> <code>WGET_TIMEOUT=120</code> </td>
			<td bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol1 twikiLastCol twikiLast"> <code>httptimeout = 120</code> (I think?) </td>
		</tr></table>
</td>
</tr>
<tr class="twikinetWrapperTableRow">
<td class="twikinetWrapperTableB twikinetWrapperTableBL"></td>
<td class="twikinetWrapperTableB twikinetWrapperTableBR"></td>
</tr>
</table>
<p />
See also <code>/usr/share/doc/fetch-crl3-*/fetch-crl.conf.example</code>
<p />
